This paper focuses on developing a machine learning-based automatic text summarization method for A-133 Single Audits, which involves text preprocessing, clustering, and sentence extraction. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
